    <p>• An ex gra­tia pay­ment of $30,000 will be given to firms clos­ing down. Firms can ap­ply for this through the SNBA, from now till March 31 next year.</p>
    <p>• Firms can also seek fi­nan­cial sup­port for one month in re­trench­ment ben­e­fits to be paid to lo­cal em­ploy­ees. This is capped at $3,000 per lo­cal em­ployee.</p>

